{"tid":2381190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓左膠黨主席害人終害己，左膠女：你唔死我點上位！","createTime":"2021-01-26T11:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-26T11:59:00.000Z","uid":219635,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a28033918ed70e873a349f80ecb4e1d33e17071d","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:43:34.000Z","msg":"韓國廣播公司KBS報道，南韓在野正義黨黨主席金鐘哲被指性騷擾一名女黨友，他接受正義黨內部調查時對性騷擾事件直認不諱，被解除黨主席職務，事件為南韓政壇投下震撼彈，外界認為可能會令標榜以性別平等的正義黨出現滅黨危機。<br />\n<br />\n事件受害人是33歲的張惠英，她在去年當選，是國會最年輕議員之一，一上任就草擬反歧視法案，為不同性別、種族、年齡、性取向及宗教人士爭取權益。她早前向正義黨投訴，上月與黨主席金鐘哲因公務出席一場晚宴，在離開餐廳時遭到性騷擾，她在三天後決定通報正義黨。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">政治立場偏左的正義黨一直標榜性別平等，提倡進步理念價值觀，是國會第三大黨，擁有六個議席。有分析認為今次事件在政壇掀起軒然大波，甚至可能令正義黨滅黨。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=421760\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421760&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=6e7d1d98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421760&h=5394d8fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=421760</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKAhUaN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKAhUaN.png&h=edc791b2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52a0995887b29ca3483703bc4c0b2d8c29803f11","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"可能係左膠女想上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一鋪收你皮，再搞到自己食哂你政黨的票，一人獨大。<br />\n相信好快到美國白左，左膠黨敗燈，到時比賀黑婆老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c8e0873d218884b41d9d6812bc81bf56ecd69b","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b5168cbd2bc417e517204e17d23e8ad12b1014","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe090540d7df796a9a33a957d37a8cbad0ded337","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56392eb78ed75e52e6fcbecf31c08168d272bb84","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a705146a394d14ffab5d741858ec3a646751a9","tid":2381190,"uid":228894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:47:30.000Z","msg":"似姚子鈴"},{"pid":"5a8ac3d480323987f43e883578dc06dcae32eb3e","tid":2381190,"uid":35891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"條女咁似表哥既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfa53ecc6c25490e863d4f084419539a99378cd","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a8ac3d480323987f43e883578dc06dcae32eb3e","tid":2381190,"uid":35891,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"條女咁似表哥既<img 