sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a1e66bdb5fc703de6fcfff24fa880f62f096f1","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1d1623d490d01494ae14edd38b95e2195457be","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f9c8e07419faf3644b225586466d43db3a66f4","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0beec8b5a65e74a3c3b241ec9ef9ee06e9e052","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148d1fb2b3b2867c6ea6b5ce316947cac66a6754","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d971367ed9e07d03c0bd508eb08c30f503288f1","tid":2381190,"uid":80814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"昨日（25日）震撼韓國的消息之一，為韓國第三大黨正義黨黨魁金鍾哲，因涉嫌性騷擾同黨議員張惠英而遭解除黨魁一職。正義黨副黨魁裴福柱（배복주 音譯）也在今日（26日），針對金鍾哲的性騷擾案做出聲明，除了回答媒體發問之外，同時也對金鍾哲的行為表示強力譴責。<br />\n<br />\n針對為何這起性騷擾案件在事發後近10天後，才於媒體公開的理由，裴副黨魁表示，本月15日，金鍾哲與張惠英因業務而聚餐，在離開餐廳時發生性騷擾案，張惠英議員於18日進行黨內申訴後，黨內堅持非公開調查的原因，便是為了避免調查過程中，發生被害者的二度傷害，同時也希望能最大限度地尊重受害者，也不希望發生事實被扭曲、無法完整表達立場的情況。&nbsp;&nbsp; 外界對金鍾哲具體的性騷擾內容感到好奇，裴副黨魁也斬釘截鐵地表示「這就是性騷擾」。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n 同時，也因加害者（金鍾哲）已承認自己性騷擾，不公開案發過程也是不希望外界以個人認知去解讀行為是否為性騷擾，模糊了事件本質，更不希望公開性騷擾過程，而再次傷害被害者。<br />\n<br />\n也有人對本起性騷擾案件過程，詢問是否涉及飲酒、醉後失態，副黨魁再次強調「就是性騷擾案件，與飲酒無關」。&nbsp;&nbsp; <span class=\"red\">裴副黨魁反問，如果被害者是喝了酒去做這些行為，就會被追問「為何喝酒了呢？」；若沒喝酒，又會被問「為何會做出這種事」，甚至也有些人會以加害者喝醉了酒，來縮小加害行為，讓這樣的性犯罪被包裝成「單純失誤」。&nbsp;&nbsp; 因此本起案件索性不公開細節，表明正義黨針對是否飲酒與否，都不會區分性騷擾案件的本質。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.creatrip.com/blog/9695\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.creatrip.com%2Fblog%2F9695&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv8tNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=42ee3d99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.creatrip.com/blog/9695</a><br />\n<br />\n如果佢哋雙重標準，嚴人寬己就話害人啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"52a0995887b29ca3483703bc4c0b2d8c29803f11","tid":2381190,"uid":219635,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:46:09.000Z","msg":"可能係左膠女想上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一鋪收你皮，再搞到自己食哂你政黨的票，一人獨大。<br />\n相信好快到美國白左，左膠黨敗燈，到時比賀黑婆老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}